From f213d05850fafe12196fa642d5e2766293dc3f38 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <claude@anthropic.com>
Date: Sat, 4 Apr 2026 23:42:49 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: replace HLS built-in player with mpv via
 tauri-plugin-mpv
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Add tauri-plugin-mpv (JSON IPC) to Cargo.toml
- Add tauri-plugin-mpv-api to package.json
- Register mpv plugin in lib.rs Tauri builder
- Add mpv:default permission to capabilities
- New MpvPlayer.vue component (controls mpv via IPC)
- Update FileSelector.vue: emit 'play' event instead of open_in_player
- Integrate MpvPlayer in App.vue with play/close/error handlers

mpv plays MKV/HEVC/AC3/DTS/ASS natively — no ffmpeg transcoding needed.
Stream URL from librqbit goes directly to mpv.
